Vendora – Full-Scale E-commerce Website
Vendora is a production-ready, multi-page e-commerce website built and owned by BytePulseX Solutions. This frontend solution is ideal for client delivery, resale, or portfolio demonstration.
It includes 18 fully designed pages covering the complete online store experience: product browsing, static listings, cart and wishlist management, user authentication, checkout flow, order tracking, and a user dashboard. Every page is responsive, interactive, and professionally structured for real-world deployment.
Key Features:
Static product listings and category-based browsing
Interactive product detail pages
Cart and wishlist management
User authentication (Register / Login)
Checkout flow with order summary
Order confirmation and order tracking pages
User dashboard layout
Responsive design for multiple devices
Extensive JavaScript-based UI interactions
Perfect For:
Designers or developers looking for a ready-to-use e-commerce template
Portfolio or demo projects
Reselling or white-label client projects
Tech Stack: HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, Vanilla JavaScript
